{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":93,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ba_feng_han","speaker_name":"跋锋寒","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"曲傲你锐气已泄，信心尽失，待会别给伏骞趁机宰掉。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":155,"line_start":42,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":"char_song_shi_dao","text":"这位兄台的剑使得不错，未知高姓大名？","tone":"疑问","chapter":155,"line_start":62,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_song_shi_dao","speaker_name":"宋师道","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"曲老师不知也罢，那动起手来将更不须顾忌。","tone":"认真","chapter":155,"line_start":66,"line_end":68},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":null,"text":"好！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":155,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_qu_ao","speaker_name":"曲傲","listener":null,"text":"来者何人？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":155,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_fu_qian","speaker_name":"伏骞","listener":"char_qu_ao","text":"本人伏骞，曲老师诚如锋寒兄所言，锐气已泄，伏骞胜之不武。何不另选决战之期，今晚我们只风花雪月，静心欣赏尚小姐冠绝天下的色艺，曲老师意下如何呢？","tone":"豪迈","chapter":155,"line_start":84,"line_end":88}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[{"id":"loc_jing_nian_chan_yuan","name":"净念禅院","region":"洛阳城南郊","one_line":"城外南郊的佛门禅院，和氏璧可能藏匿之处","source_refs":[{"chapter":155,"line_start":96,"line_end":96,"text":"目的地是城外南郊的净念禅院。"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
